name: CV Baker
body:
### CV Baker's here to help
CV Baker makes delicious cakes out of your CV data. You can have a HTML cake, a PDF cake and even a docx cake for further enhancements. 

Right now, the project is still in development, but you can help:

```
$ instruction 1 
```
tagline: A Website to generate a nice CV with a lot of interlinks and nice stuff
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
